1:11:50.640 --> 1:11:53.120
Dad... Dad, come out, come out!

1:11:54.360 --> 1:11:55.960
Dad, it's me.

1:12:10.000 --> 1:12:11.640
Did Polly send you?

1:12:13.480 --> 1:12:15.960
Did Polly send you?

1:12:15.960 --> 1:12:17.360
