1:12:17.360 --> 1:12:18.640
No.

1:12:20.920 --> 1:12:23.320
You're not dead.

1:12:23.320 --> 1:12:25.520
You're not even sick.

1:12:25.520 --> 1:12:27.000
But I am, my darling.

1:12:28.920 --> 1:12:30.360
I'm sick.

1:12:31.560 --> 1:12:33.000
Sick like you was.

1:12:33.000 --> 1:12:35.200
No. Not true.

1:12:35.200 --> 1:12:38.000
I know it.
You've got to live, Daddy.

1:12:40.720 --> 1:12:42.800
You let the fire go out.

1:12:44.880 --> 1:12:47.520
Light the fire again
and get warm,

1:12:47.520 --> 1:12:50.680
and you will see
that you must live.

1:13:52.960 --> 1:13:55.680
You're not even sick, Daddy.

1:13:55.680 --> 1:13:57.720
