1:14:32.160 --> 1:14:34.240
Fucking Gypsies.

1:14:42.360 --> 1:14:44.680
Have you thrown the tinkers off
the top field yet?

1:14:44.680 --> 1:14:47.560
Well, I went up to the caravan,
sir, but there was no-one there.

1:14:47.560 --> 1:14:50.080
Well, go back up there
and set fire to the fucking thing.

1:14:50.080 --> 1:14:52.040
Yes, sir.

1:14:57.720 --> 1:15:00.600
