with petrol?

1:15:07.680 --> 1:15:10.880
I said, have you filled the car up
with petrol?

1:15:14.320 --> 1:15:16.360
How was the wedding in Berlin?

1:15:18.880 --> 1:15:21.520
I hear Chancellor Hitler
himself was the best man.

1:15:24.040 --> 1:15:27.240
You've been my doctor now
for three years.

1:15:28.880 --> 1:15:31.400
Never knew you were
so well connected.

1:15:31.400 --> 1:15:33.840
Oh, and the doctor
at St Thomas's

1:15:33.840 --> 1:15:35.920
who you sent me to
for the second opinion,

1:15:35.920 --> 1:15:37.960
second set of X-rays?

1:15:37.960 --> 1:15:41.600
A maid of honour
at the same wedding.

1:15:41.600 --> 1:15:43.520
All so very well fucking
connected.

1:15:45.680 --> 1:15:47.400
On your knees, Holford.

1:15:53.560 --> 1:15:56.040
I'm guessing you people
all decided

1:15:56.040 --> 1:15:58.400
that the only person

1:15:58.400 --> 1:16:01.720
who could ever kill
Tommy Shelby

1:16:01.720 --> 1:16:03.640
is Tommy Shelby himself.

1:16:06.720 --> 1:16:09.160
You made me believe
death was coming.

1:16:09.160 --> 1:16:11.680
Let my nature do the rest,
eh?

1:16:16.680 --> 1:16:20.280
You may not have tuberculoma,
Mr Shelby,

1:16:20.280 --> 1:16:21.920
but you are sick.

1:16:23.160 --> 1:16:24.640
I know you.

1:16:25.840 --> 1:16:27.880
You are sick with guilt.

1:16:29.640 --> 1:16:32.640
Sick of death at your own hand.

1:16:34.120 --> 1:16:35.880
Sick of who you were.

1:16:38.720 --> 1:16:40.520
You are no longer
the kind of man

1:16:40.520 --> 1:16:42.920
who would kill another man
in cold blood.

1:16:48.680 --> 1:16:52.960
Tommy, you have been
on a journey

1:16:52.960 --> 1:16:56.480
from the backstreets
to the corridors of power.

1:16:59.040 --> 1:17:00.640
You cannot go back.

1:17:02.040 --> 1:17:03.920
You are a different man.

1:17:05.480 --> 1:17:08.000
The gun no longer belongs
in your hand.

1:17:14.400 --> 1:17:16.200
Oh, but I am back.

1:17:19.080 --> 1:17:21.600
Back from under the ground.

1:17:22.680 --> 1:17:24.480
Close your eyes.

